[EN]
Promotional text:
PointFinder turns Pathfinder games into immersive digital adventures. Check in at real-world bases with NFC and solve challenges with your team.

Description:
PointFinder is the companion app for NFC-powered Pathfinder missions and outdoor challenge games.
Whether you are a player in the field or an operator running the event, PointFinder connects teams, bases, and live progress in real time.

For players:
Join a game with a QR code or join code
Explore base locations on the map
Check in at physical bases with NFC
Unlock and solve text or photo challenges
Keep playing offline and sync actions when your connection returns
Track progress by base status, from not visited to completed

For operators:
Sign in to access your games or collaborate on games with other operators
Monitor teams and base activity on a live map
View team progress and submission status for each base
Write and link NFC tags to bases from your iPhone

Built for real-world events:
Designed for Pathfinder organizations, camps, and mission activities
Multi-language support: English, Portuguese, and German
Push notifications and resilient sync for active games

Important:
A game code from your organizer is required to join as a player.
An operator account is required to use operator tools.
NFC features require a compatible iPhone.
Location access is used during active missions for map and team tracking.
Photo submissions require an internet connection.

